*DESCRIPTION_START
People scurry about this room performing a number of clerical duties. Filing cabinets cover the wall space. Unfiled papers have been placed in large stacks everywhere. It is amazing that anyone can work in this cluttered environment.  In one corner is an opening that is labelled OOC INFORMATION.
