NUMBER 340
NAME Lockup
region 103
channel 103
FIXED_LIGHT
outofbody
*DESCRIPTION_START
This cold, stone chamber is totally devoid of any comforts. A pile of musty hay serves as a bed, and a single bucket filled with rancid smelling water sits in one corner. Next to the bucket a mangy rat nibbles on a solitary piece of half-eaten bread. The bread has a fuzzy, putrid moldy growth on it. A stout, iron door separates you from freedom, but no lock is even visible on this side. Scrawled on the walls are the inane ramblings of previous occupants.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 946 ADJ1=169 VAL2=338 LOCKED
